&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;​    1.ATTACK [PTsecurity] Drupalgeddon2 &amp;lt;8.3.9 &amp;lt;8.4.6 &amp;lt;8.5.1 RCE through registration form (CVE-2018-7600) [Priority: 1] {PROTO:006} 172.17.0.6:51702 -&amp;gt; 172.17.0.1:8080&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;​    2.Possible Drupalgeddon2 attack [Priority: 3] {PROTO:006} 172.17.0.6:51702 -&amp;gt; 172.17.0.1:8080&lt;/p&gt;
